Hi everyone, I'm your friend from another place in the world.
How are you today? Why you feel so down?
I'm so sorry there's language barrier, but i will tell something the best i can. 
The first time we decided to walking this journey, i feel so strong till i get too much ambitious. But then, everytime i falling down, i get up by myself again and again until i feel too tired of this all. Sitting on the bench at the riverside, sun setting warm up my heart. Now i know, how hard i try to run after this world race, it never enough my heart so much in pain, an then I'll decide to not too hard to myself it heals everything. So to you, my friend who reads this comment, wish you good life. Greetings from me. 
I live in your hearts.
